title: Ep.1: Packers Blowout, Steelers Comeback, Apple Cup Predictions, Rookie Debuts, and More.
description: In this episode we discuss how the packers will bounce back from their embarrassing loss and how impressive the steelers comeback was. This could also be the year WSU beats UW in the apple cup. We later discuss Trevor Lawrence, Zach Wilson, Trey Lance, Justin Fields, and even Joe Tryon.
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
